  <brief_title>The Role of Audiovisual Biofeedback on Image Quality During 4D Anatomic and Functional Imaging</brief_title>
  <official_title>Investigating the Role of Audiovisual Biofeedback on Image Quality During 4D Anatomic and Functional Imaging</official_title>
  <sponsors>
